org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.transport.fix

Class FIXTransportSender

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.core.config.AbstractConfigurationElement
      • org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.transport.base.AbstractTransportSender
        • org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.transport.fix.FIXTransportSender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationElement, org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanNameAware

    public class FIXTransportSender
extends AbstractTransportSender

    FIX transport sender

    Fix initiator [default] properties should be defined for this instance

    • reconnectInterval - Time between reconnection attempts in seconds
    • heartBeatInterval - Heartbeat interval in seconds
    • startTime - Time of day in the format of HH:MM:SS that this FIX session becomes activated
    • endTime - Time of day in the format of HH:MM:SS that this FIX session becomes deactivated
    • messageStoreFactory - MessageStore that Quickfix/j uses to store messages. Depending on type of storage method define a spring bean and set a reference of it to this parameter. eg: type of messageStoreFactory beans are FileMessageStoreFactoryImpl,JDBCMessageStoreFactoryImpl
    • logFactory - LogFactory that Quickfix/j uses to keep logs. Depending on log store method define a spring bean and set a reference of it to this parameter eg: type of logFactory beans are FileLogFactoryImpl, JDBCLogFactoryImpl
    • otherSettings - Other optional initiator configuration settings provided by Quickfix/j
